Package: joinkit
Title: KIT Multi-Wave Data Join Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("KIT", "Join Tool", email = "joinkit@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shiny application for joining multi-wave survey data (CSV and
    SPSS SAV). Launch with \code{run_joinkit()}. Supports join keys,
    suffixes, join methods,
    post-join validation, and export to CSV or SAV.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    bslib,
    dplyr,
    haven,
    purrr,
    readr,
    shiny
LazyData: true
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
